{
  "id": "nce4-l11",
  "title": "Lesson 11: How to Grow Old",
  "audio": "/audio/nce4/11ÔºçHow to Grow Old.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 11",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.4,
      "endTime": 2.43
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How to grow old",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.44,
      "endTime": 10.59
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What, according to the author, is the best way to overcome the fear of death as you get older?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "endTime": 20.21
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Some old people are oppressed by the fear of death.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.22,
      "endTime": 25.13
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In the young there is a justification for this feeling.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.14,
      "endTime": 28.82
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Young men who have reason to fear that they will be killed in battle",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.83,
      "endTime": 33.23
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "may justifiably feel bitter in the thought",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.24,
      "endTime": 36.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "that they have been cheated of the best things that life has to offer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.79,
      "endTime": 42.44
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But in an old man who has known human joys and sorrows,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.45,
      "endTime": 48.11
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and has achieved whatever work it was in him to do,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 48.12,
      "endTime": 52
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the fear of death is somewhat abject and ignoble.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.01,
      "endTime": 56.92
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The best way to overcome it--so at least it seems to me--",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.93,
      "endTime": 62.66
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "is to make your interests gradually wider and more impersonal,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 62.67,
      "endTime": 68.04
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "until bit by bit the walls of the ego recede,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 68.05,
      "endTime": 73.21
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and your life becomes increasingly merged in the universal life.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.22,
      "endTime": 77.72
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "An individual human existence should be like a river--",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.73,
      "endTime": 83.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "small at first, narrowly contained within its banks,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 83.51,
      "endTime": 88.41
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and rushing passionately past boulders and over waterfalls.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.42,
      "endTime": 93.69
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Gradually the river grows wider, the banks recede, the waters flow more quietly,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 93.7,
      "endTime": 101.17
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and in the end, without any visiblebreak, they become merged in the sea,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.18,
      "endTime": 107.43
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and painlessly lose their individual being.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 107.44,
      "endTime": 111.18
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The man who, in old age can see his life in this way,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 111.19,
      "endTime": 116.76
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "will not suffer from the fear of death,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116.77,
      "endTime": 119.53
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "since the things he cares for will continue.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 119.54,
      "endTime": 123.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "And if, with the decay of vitality, weariness increases,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 123.38,
      "endTime": 130.51
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the thought of rest will be not unwelcome.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 130.52,
      "endTime": 134.28
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I should wish to die while still at work,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 134.29,
      "endTime": 137.81
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "knowing that others will carry on what I can no longer do,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 137.82,
      "endTime": 142.35
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and content in the thought that what was possible has been done.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 142.36,
      "endTime": 147.36
    }
  ]
}